          <p>Senior students and postgrads offer tutoring sessions for core CS modules. Weekly sessions available during semester.</p>
          <a href="mailto:undergrad@cs.sun.ac.za" class="cs-res-support__link">Enquire about tutoring &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-res-support__card">
          <div class="cs-res-support__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" width="30" height="30"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Computer Labs</h4>
          <p>Access to dedicated CS labs with Linux and Windows workstations, high-speed internet, and printing facilities.</p>
          <span class="cs-res-support__detail">GEB Building, Floor 3 &mdash; Open 08:00&ndash;22:00</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-res-support__card">
          <div class="cs-res-support__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" width="30" height="30"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Mental Health &amp; Wellbeing</h4>
          <p>Stellenbosch University offers free counselling and support services for all registered students.</p>
          <a href="https://www.sun.ac.za/cscd" target="_blank" class="cs-res-support__link">SU Counselling Centre &nearr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-res-support__card">
          <div class="cs-res-support__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" width="30" height="30"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 015.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h4>IT Helpdesk</h4>
          <p>Technical support for campus Wi-Fi, lab access, email issues, and software installations.</p>
          <a href="mailto:tech@cs.sun.ac.za" class="cs-res-support__link">Contact IT Support &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

